# Secrets for local CI runs with `act`. Copy this file to `.secrets` (which is
# gitignored) and fill in the value, then run `just act`.
#
# NIX_GITHUB_TOKEN — a CLASSIC GitHub PAT with `repo` scope. nix uses it as an
# access-token to fetch the workflow's private flake inputs (muse, termite-chat)
# as well as the public ones. Mint at https://github.com/settings/tokens
# (classic). This mirrors the server-side `secrets.NIX_GITHUB_TOKEN`.
NIX_GITHUB_TOKEN=
